

Tall (~7 ft), almost pink skin, sharp exaggerated features, knotted hair, antlers peeking through.

Emerged from the Great Pine once the site was cleared of the wisps

Told Tod that his Wife gave him his powers.
Her spirit resides in the feywild, and between the two, there is an innate connection that spans the planes.

Seek these other great trees - former sites of Feywild connections - focus your heart.
